{{Messages|text=
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' (Trailblazer), I heard about a new hotpot store. It's packed with people and has a snaking queue
:{Choice} You can still use your phone?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' You can still use your phone? I heard you got injured.
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' It's just a scratch
:{Choice} Are your eyes alright?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Really? Your eyes are fine now?
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 16 Jiaoqiu 04.png|80px]]
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Don't worry, someone is accompanying me
:{Choice} Doesn't seem I need to be worried then!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Really? Well, I was worried about nothing!
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 16 Jiaoqiu 04.png|80px]]
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Don't worry, someone is accompanying me
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' It won't impede my attempts at exploring a new hotpot place
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' I heard about a hotpot place that's been blowing up recently and is packed full of customers every day.
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' I heard the store signature is the "Tea Hotpot with Pickled Pepper and Chili Oil". There's only a limited amount sold every day. Do you want to try it with me?
:{Choice} Let's go! Crowds mean good food!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Let's go! Crowds mean good food!
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Let's go! Word on the street is that last night, some customers lined up till the store closed and still didn't get to eat anything
:{Choice} Tea? Chili oil? Pickled pepper?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Tea? Chili oil? Pickled pepper? Is that even edible?
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Of course. The premium tea broth is accompanied by chili oil, removing the spiciness and increasing the aroma and taste. You can have a bowl to sip before you eat, as soon as the hotpot is boiling
:{Choice} We won't queue for years, right?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' We won't have to queue for years, right?
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' It's not that bad
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Even on the Xianzhou, that much of a wait is a bit of a stretch
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Hold on, the online queue is opening. Time to fight for a number on the jade abacus
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Jiaoqiu has gone offline.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Jiaoqiu is online.
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Guess what?
:{Choice} Sounds like you didn't get it
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds like you didn't get a number. Do that many people want to eat this?
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' As long as "limited" is in the marketing, it'll go viral one way or another
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' The store is also offering a few new flavors for soup bases
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' But I'm not sure if they're palatable for you
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Coriander Hotpot
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Oof. This first one. I just can't
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' And then, there's Tomato Hotpot with Arugula
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Tallow Hotpot with Cheese
:{Choice} What if I say yes to all
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What if I say I can take them all?
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Brave warrior, I admire your courage
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' For today's meal, I'll accompany your culinary choices till the end of the world!
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Then, I'll go ahead to queue up first
:{Choice} I can't stomach this
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sorry, I really can't stomach this
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' That's too bad. Guess I'll have to go alone
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' I'll come back alive
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px]]
