===(Trailblazer), do you know...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' (Trailblazer), do you know where the Ditings on the Xianzhou Luofu usually hang out?
:{Choice} I know! Starskiff Haven docks!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I know! Starskiff Haven docks!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' March said that, if you can't find them, you can howl twice to summon them
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Howl twice... That doesn't seem like a good idea
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' I saw a Diting once at Starwatcher Avenue. It was chewing aggressively on a wooden table leg along the streets
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' It looked really cute, but unfortunately, table legs can't really withstand a Diting's teeth
:{Choice} Using table legs as chew sticks?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It must be using the table leg as a chew stick
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Truly an Artisanship Commission ingenium
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' But that table leg is tasteless despite its colors. The little Diting won't be satisfied chewing on it
:{Choice} Does the Diting need to compensate
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It broke the table leg? Did the boss get the Diting to pay for the damage?
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Yeah, the boss was fuming and said he now has a bone to pick with the Artisanship Commission
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' Luckily, I was passing by and helped it pay off the debt for the table leg
::'''Jiaoqiu:''' You could even say that the Artisanship Commission now owes me a favor
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Since I have nothing to do on the Luofu at the time, I went ahead and made differently flavored chew sticks for it as a way to kill time
:{Choice} What's the stick's flavor?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm curious. What's the stick's flavor?
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' To figure out this little fella's preference, I bought a classic flavored chew stick
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' During the refinement process, I added a little cinnamon, mint, and grated cheese
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' And of course, chili
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' I'm kidding. I just happened to be preparing some fried chilis that look like chili but don't taste spicy at all
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' There are a few leftover ingredients, just enough to make some chew sticks
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' Pity. The little one won't be getting a taste of that for a while
:'''Jiaoqiu:''' May we meet again
}}
